title: Ebro In The Morning - Wale Talks Folarin II + Is Wawa More Than A Gas Station?
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 10/28.

Wale joins the program to talk Folarin II (0:00) The crew talks about the effects of the recent Nor'easter (32), and Ebro talks about the Wawa phenomenon. (1:17)
